==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mongoloid
<hw>Mon"go*loid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Mongol</ets>
+ <ets>-oid</ets>.]</ety> <def>Resembling a Mongol or the Mongols;
having race characteristics, such as color, hair, and features, like
those of the Mongols.</def> <rj><au>Huxley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Of, related to, or affected with, <er>Down
syndrome</er>; -- not a technical term.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mongoloid</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Mongoloid
<hw>Mon"go*loid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A person affected
with <er>Down syndrome</er>; -- not a technical term.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

